4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed to train individuals with no prior knowledge into becoming cybersecurity specialists. The program spans 16 weeks, featuring three live online classes per week, accommodating up to 16 students per class. Participants will gain expertise in Windows and Linux administration, cloud security, penetration testing, and compliance with standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Graduates receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate, recognized by various institutions. The syllabus is available in both English and Spanish. For more details, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). Stop.